    <string name="help_content"><b>Welcome to Kaikanakku Pattika!</b>\n\nThis app helps you convert between the modern Metric system (centimeters) and the traditional Kerala system of \'Kol\' and \'Viral\'.\n\n<b>Features:</b>\n\n<b>Converter:</b> Use the switch at the top to select your conversion direction. Enter a value and press Convert. All conversions are saved automatically.\n\n<b>Calculator:</b> Add or subtract two different measurements in the traditional system. All calculations are saved automatically.\n\n<b>History:</b> Every conversion and calculation is saved. You can search, sort, favorite, and delete entries. Swipe an entry to delete it. Tap an entry to copy the result. Use the \'Re-use\' button to send a history item back to the converter.\n\n<b>Settings:</b> Customize the app\'s behavior, such as precision, rounding, and data management.</string>

